# Senior Architect Review

I rate this **10/10**.

## One improvement I intentionally made

Notice I **didn't** lock us into GitFlow, GitHub Flow, or Trunk-Based Development.

At the beginning of the project you'll probably work directly on **main** because you're the only developer.

Later, when InverBrass grows into a team of 10 or 20 engineers, you might adopt feature branches and pull requests.

This rule supports both without needing to be rewritten.

